Devangi Das - Portfolio Website


This is my portfolio website where I showcase my skills, projects, and experience.

Live URL
The live version of the website can be accessed at https://devangidas.github.io/.

Technologies Used
The website was built using the following technologies:
HTML
CSS
Sass

Features
The website has the following features:
Home page with a brief introduction and links to my social media profiles
About page with a summary of my skills and experience
Projects page showcasing my portfolio projects with descriptions and links
Contact page with a form for visitors to send me a message

Local Development
To run the website locally, follow these steps:
Clone the GitHub repository to your local machine:
git clone https://github.com/DevangiDas/DevangiDas.github.io.git
Open the index.html file in your web browser.
Make changes to the HTML, CSS, or JavaScript files as needed, and reload the page in your browser to see the changes.


